sentences: Peter London (born Pedrinho Londres; 28 September 1982 in Sweden) is a Swedish bassist.
Since 2015, London has been the bass-player of RAC/pop rock-band Bedårande Barn where Jimmie Åkesson plays keyboard.
London married Swedish model and former Miss Sweden title-holder Isabel Lestapier Winqvist on 25 June 2010 at the Hedvig Eleonora Church in Stockholm.
